About Riverwalk Landing
Welcome to Affordable Resort-Style
Retirement in Northwest Florida
We are now accepting reservations for move-ins, and all-ages
RV and Cottage rentals
! Please review the
Community Documents
below, and contact us with any questions.
Riverwalk Landing is a welcoming and affordable 55 and older manufactured home retirement community on the Florida Panhandle. Enjoy resort-style amenities, miles of walking trails within the securely gated community, and boating and fishing on Choctawhatchee Bay. We are just minutes from the emerald waters and beautiful white sand beaches of the Gulf of Mexico.
Riverwalk Landing is pet friendly. Family will love to visit with Destin and south Walton County offering incredible dining, shopping, golf and recreational facilities just a short drive away.

Riverwalk Village Prospectus
Every Day is A Vacation
Resort-Style Amenities
Final Construction is nearly complete! Come together at the Riverwalk Social Grill and Tiki Bar and pickleball courts! Enjoy fishing on the creek, or get out on the water from the nearby boat ramp. Riverwalk Landing is pet friendly, with miles of nature trails and dog park. The clubhouse has a kitchen, office space, and exercise room.
Learn More
Charm & Convenience
Small Town Living
Located in Freeport, Florida, Riverwalk Landing is walking distance to Publix and other essential businesses.
Explore The Area
Discover Florida's Emerald Coast!
Shopping, Dining & Beaches
Enjoy the shopping, dining, and attractions of Destin and south Walton County, Fort Walton Beach, and Panama City Beach including the Emerald Coast's famous white sand beaches!
Fishing & Boating
Onsite boat storage and the nearby boat ramp make it easy to access Four Mile Creek and Choctawhatchee Bay, where Destin's East Pass opens onto the emerald waters of the Gulf of Mexico.
Golf & Recreation
Award-winning golf courses and other recreational activities get you outside in the Florida sunshine just a few minutes from Riverwalk Landing.
Ready to live like you vacation?
